  Game information:
  =================
 
  Dr. Aiden Krone has made a Time Jump across the space-time continuum - a
  reckless act with frightening consequences. Now, a disturbing alternate
  reality has evolved within the bleak and rain-soaked Alpha District. Armed
  with the experimental Beta Suit, you alone are able to slow, stop and reverse
  the flow of time. Only with this ability can you lead the uprising to victory
  and put an end to Krone&#039;s madness.
